CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 27, 1957, pg. 24 reads: "They Had A Ball - The young set had a ball at the Alpha picnic Friday. One of the main attractions at the park is the tower in background.  Resting after coming down from the tower are Grant Farmer, Rose Alyce Cephas, Lorraine Goggins, Joyce Ann Robinson, Regis Goggins, and Roger Thomas. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Grant Farmer, Rose Alyce Cephas, Lorraine Goggins, Joyce Ann Robinson, Regis Goggins, and Roger Thomas, posed in front of tower during Alpha picnic
